#: ckanext/harvest/templates/source/new_source_form.html:95
msgid "Confirmation of this will delete the federation source and all federated datasets in federation tasks carried out. Warning: if you delete this source, as well as the federated datasets, you will also be deleting all previous task reports. Do this if you want to delete both the source and federated datasets and create a new source to federate new datasets. Are you sure you want to delete this federation source and all federated datasets?"
msgstr "A confirmación desta acción eliminará a fonte de federación e todos os conxuntos de datos federados nas tarefas de federación realizadas. Advertencia: se elimina esta fonte, ademais dos conxuntos de datos federados, eliminará tamén todos os informes de tarefas anteriores. Utilice esta acción se desexa eliminar a fonte e os conxuntos de datos federados, e desexa crear unha nova fonte para federar novos conxuntos de datos. Está seguro de que quere eliminar esta fonte de federación e todos os conxuntos de datos federados?"

#: ckanext/harvest/templates/source/new_source_form.html:96
msgid "Confirmation of this will delete the federation source but keep all federated datasets in previous tasks. Warning: if you delete this source and create a new one that contains already federated datasets, twice as many data sheets will be published on the portal. You should only do this if you want to delete the source and reassign the federated datasets to another publisher (in this case, please inform soporte@datos.gob.es). Are you sure you want to delete this federation source and keep the federated datasets?"
msgstr "A confirmación desta acción eliminará a fonte de federación pero manterá todos os conxuntos de datos federados en tarefas anteriores. Advertencia: se elimina esta fonte e crea unha nova que conteña os datasets xa federados duplicaranse os datasets publicados no portal. Recoméndase usar esta opción só se desexa eliminar a fonte e reatribuír os conxuntos de datos federados a outro publicador (neste caso, rogamos comunique esta circunstancia a soporte@datos.gob.es). Está seguro de que quere eliminar esta fonte de federación e manter os datasets federados?"

